Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:37.89,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}讓心放寬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:43.66,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}希望這種歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:50.84,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:58.67,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無垠的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:03.49,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}充滿了愛與希望
